category: Libs
requires: libgcc1 libstdc++6
external-source: libsigc2.0
sdesc: "C++ typesafe callback library (runtime library)"
ldesc: "libsigc++ implements a typesafe callback system for standard 
C++. It allows you to define signals and to connect those signals to any
callback function, either global or a member function, regardless of
whether it is static or virtual."
